Class UserPageInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • DTO.UserPageInfo

  • public class UserPageInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    The class UserPageInfo holds the data of a page of users. It also contains information whether this page any next page or previous page and also the contains the page number member.
